Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast.

Name: Rocky Mountain Chocolate Factory
Description: Sells really good caramel apples and a lot of other chocolates.

Name: Fish Hopper
Description: Really good sea food restaurant. There are also lots of other fun little stores and restaurants nearby. It's right on the beach/shore.

Name: The Getty
Description: An art museum with lots of works from famous artists. The place features works from pre-20th century Europe;19th-20th century American, European and Asian photographs; and contemporary and modern sculpture

Name: Calaveras Big Trees State Park
Description: As per the name, there are some wickedly big trees here. It's a fun place if you like a little hiking and feeling small in nature.

Description: A place that offers tours of the set where the Hobbit movies took place. I've never been but it sounds like a really cool place.
